<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> projectorion, yales: You two are having lots of fun bludgeoning each other, but neither of you seems to be citing much in the way of facts.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
